Party Makeup

If you’re planning a trip to a special event and need an expert like Zohara Shereen who can help you look your absolute best, you’ve come to the right place! From fashion and makeup advice to special occasion dresses and accessories, She can give you the red-carpet treatment with one of her party packages. Whether you choose from one of her natural and elegant or hi-octane glamour options, they’ll be styled with plenty of impeccable details.

Choose Our Signature Party Makeup Services

Step into the spotlight with confidence and grace. At [Your Brand Name], we believe in more than just makeup; we believe in transformation. Our team of professional artists is dedicated to bringing out the best in you, ensuring that you not only look, but also feel like the star of the show. Whether it’s a glamorous gala or a casual soirée, trust in our party makeup services to leave a lasting impression.

  • Luxury Product Range
  • Tailored for You
  • Trend-aware Techniques

Experience the unmatched benefits:

Choosing the right party makeup artist is crucial, not just for the flawless finish but also for the peace of mind they bring. Opting for a professional means they’ll not only keep to the schedule, ensuring punctuality for your big event, but also let you relish in the luxury of relaxation. So, why stress and spend hours striving for perfection, when you can simply sit back, unwind, and emerge looking your radiant best?

  • Quick & Stunning Transformations
  • Weather-Proof & Smudge-Resistant
  • Designed to Highlight Your Features

Portfolio

Bridal Pre Wedding Party Make Up Celebrity And Commercial Photoshoot

Party Makeup

What do your party makeover packages include?

Every package is inclusive of makeup, hairdo and styling. The best of makeup products, hair appliances and the personalized attention of Zohara and her team is guaranteed for every client.

What brands of makeup products do you use?

We use only the best of products,internationally renowned brands such as MAC, Huda Beauty, Dior, Morphe, Anastasia Beverly Hills and so much more. Products are carefully chosen according to the clients skin type, sensitivity and preference, making sure every look is long-lasting and perfect.

What is the main difference between the simple party and glam party makeover packages?

The simple party makeover is subtle and natural looking, while the glam party makeover package is for a bolder and more elaborate look. The glam party makeover takes more time and has more steps, and is therefore more expensive but so very worth it if you’re stepping out for a luxurious event.

What does Zohara Shereen offer that other makeup artists don’t?

All makeup artists are masters of their craft and it’s your call as to who you trust and feel comfortable with. What we promise to do is collaborate with you to create a look that is beautiful and won’t need retouching, and will look gorgeous on camera as well. Our top priority is your comfort and your makeup desires!

What are the benefits of choosing Zohara Shereen as my bridal makeup artist?
From a base that won’t budge to perfectly blended eyes, she knows what you need for your big event. Her clients are always raving about her ability to blur imperfections, find the perfect shade, and create literal art all at the same time. So if you’re looking for an experienced artist who can give you long-lasting, insta-worthy makeup perfection, you’ve come to the right place.
